Anna Yuryevna Netrebko (born 18 September 1971) is an operatic soprano. She now holds dual Russian and Austrian citizenship and currently resides in Vienna. She has been nicknamed &quot;La Bellissima&quot; by fans.  &lt;a href=&quot;
